{"tid":2188802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那艦隊首度接近夏威夷","createTime":"2020-09-04T12:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T13:18:10.000Z","uid":358431,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c4a09ec1c3384f44ebba3e2563064df5dffc8c","tid":2188802,"uid":358431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:49:08.000Z","msg":"日本產經新聞今天引述台灣國防部1日送交立法院的中國軍力年度報告指出，中國南海艦隊今年初穿越第二島鏈，首度接近包含夏威夷在內的第三島鏈區域並在附近演習。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，夏威夷是美軍印度太平洋司令部所在地，中國藉此展示已有能力突破美國關島與日本小笠原諸島等組成的第二島鏈，直指夏威夷的戰略據點。中國海軍南海艦隊的遠航艦隊，今年初「首度接近第三島鏈，對外展示具有突破（第一、第二）島鏈封鎖、實行遠洋作戰的實力」。<br />\n<br />\n報告書提到，共軍以此檢視在遠離中國本土海域的指揮管制以及長時間航海、海上艦艇整備能力等。中國海軍已不單能威脅關島，還能威脅到更遠的夏威夷。<br />\n<br />\n汁: <a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2574758/台國防部指中國艦隊首度接近夏威夷?fbclid=IwAR0cFvMdqxpjPiKBSEPmoyTWNs0PuWXEM6-MperRD3lHCN9spqnw0ngmIRY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2574758%2F%E5%8F%B0%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%89%A6%E9%9A%8A%E9%A6%96%E5%BA%A6%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%91%E5%A4%8F%E5%A8%81%E5%A4%B7%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0cFvMdqxpjPiKBSEPmoyTWNs0PuWXEM6-MperRD3lHCN9spqnw0ngmIRY&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=b4bfcd12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2574758/台國防部指中國艦隊首度接近夏威夷?fbclid=IwAR0cFvMdqxpjPiKBSEPmoyTWNs0PuWXEM6-MperRD3lHCN9spqnw0ngmIRY</a>"},{"pid":"8a1d18163a908f779650043b15778f29354bd0d3","tid":2188802,"uid":362431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:50:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d65ac629cb0e343a88d5172693740a475a1023e","tid":2188802,"uid":167597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:51:01.000Z","msg":"人地俾你出，就以為贏左"},{"pid":"96631fd35f48334b13c9b47b2776602d8491311f","tid":2188802,"uid":358431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T12:51:34.000Z","msg":"信報新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\